{"article_id":"R2kqFxRJkBdnmPeP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Commerce Secretary John Bryson said Monday","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"he will take a medical leave of absence","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to undergo tests and evaluations","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"after suffering a seizure in connection with a succession of traffic accidents in the Los Angeles area .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Mr. Bryson informed President Obama","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that he was taking a medical leave","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"\" so that I can focus all of my attention on resolving the health issues","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that arose over the weekend , \"","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"according to a statement","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"released by the department .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Deputy Secretary Rebecca Blank will serve as acting commerce secretary in Mr. Bryson ' s absence .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"White House press secretary Jay Carney said in a statement","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"that Obama ' s thoughts were with Mr. Bryson and his family .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"The 68-year-old former utility executive struck a car","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"stopped for a train","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"- twice -","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"on Saturday afternoon","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and then rammed into another vehicle with his car a few minutes later .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"He was found unconscious in his vehicle ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"and government officials said Monday","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"he had had a seizure ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"which could play a role in whether he ' s charged with felony hit-and-run .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"It wasn ' t clear whether the medical episode preceded or followed the collisions ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"but Mr. Bryson hasn ' t suffered a seizure before ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"said a department official","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"who spoke on condition of anonymity","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to discuss the secretary ' s medical history .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Mr. Bryson has a \" limited recall of the events , \"","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"the official said .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"The crashes drew attention","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"because of health concerns","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"involving a member of Obama ' s Cabinet ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"as well as the challenge","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"investigators face","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"when trying to determine whether someone should be held criminally responsible","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"because of adverse health .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Mr. Bryson was driving alone in a Lexus in San Gabriel , a community of about 40,000 northeast of Los Angeles ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"when he struck the rear of a vehicle","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that had stopped for a passing train ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"authorities said .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"He spoke briefly with the three occupants","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"and then hit their car again","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"as he departed ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"investigators said .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"They followed him","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"while calling police .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"He was cited for felony hit-and-run ,","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"although he has not been charged .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"Mr. Bryson then struck a second car in the nearby city of Rosemead ,","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"where he was found unconscious in his car ,","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"authorities said .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"Mr. Bryson has returned to Washington after a brief hospital stay ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"department spokeswoman Jennifer Friedman said .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Officials said","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. Bryson was not on state business ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"was driving a personal car","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"and did not have a security detail at the time .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"He took a Breathalyzer test","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that didn ' t detect any alcohol ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"but investigators were awaiting the results from a blood test ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"said Los Angeles County sheriff ' s Capt . Mike Parker .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Commerce officials said","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"he was given medication","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"to treat the seizure .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Paramedics treated two people in the first collision for pain ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"but a couple","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"involved in the second crash","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"declined medical aid .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"The case was being reviewed by sheriff ' s investigators","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and will likely be submitted to prosecutors in the coming days .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"\" In most cases , it is presented to the DA ' s office","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to make a decision , \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"sheriff ' s Lt. Margarito Robles said .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Defense attorney Steve Meister ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"who has represented people","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"who have been involved in crashes","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"while having seizures ,","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"\" it ' s difficult to assign criminal liability","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"when someone was medically unconscious .","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"They have to be aware what was happening . \"","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"The episode is consistent with someone","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"who has suffered a series of epileptic seizures ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"said Dr. Jerome Engel Jr. , a neurologist at the University of California , Los Angeles ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"who is not involved in Mr. Bryson ' s care .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"After a seizure , a person is often confused ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"and that state of confusion can last for a while .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"\" You may even seem to be alert and awake ,","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"but you ' re not really behaving normally , \"","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"Dr. Engel said .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Under California law , a doctor has to report a patient","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"who complains of lapses of consciousness","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"or whose epileptic seizures pose an impairment to driving .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"In those cases , a person can ' t drive","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"unless he ' s been seizure-free for three months .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Mr. Bryson had been in California","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"to deliver the commencement address Thursday at Pasadena Polytechnic School ,","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"where his four children attended .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"The K-12 school said","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"he urged students to pursue their passions ,","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"to serve their country , and to value their education and friendships .","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"Mr. Bryson was sworn in to lead the Commerce Department in October","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"after easily overcoming conservatives ' objections","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"that his pro-environmental views made him unsuited for the job .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"As secretary , Mr. Bryson is a member of the president ' s economic team","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"and has advised on energy issues .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"He is the former head of Edison International , the holding company","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"that owns Southern California Edison ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"and has served on boards of major corporations ,","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"including the Boeing Co. and the Walt Disney Co .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"He helped oversee Edison ' s transformation into a leading wind and solar company","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"and launched a plan","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"to turn 65 million square feet of unused commercial rooftops into solar power stations with enough electricity for more than 160,000 homes .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":227,"left":0,"right":226,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":226,"left":208,"right":225,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":126,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":124,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":117,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":116,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":1,"right":115,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":115,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":120,"right":121,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":118,"right":119,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":141,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":134,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":131,"right":133,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":129,"right":130,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":128,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"